Component Structure:

React components are replaced with PHP includes and Bootstrap components

Instead of props, we use PHP variables and loops

Styling:

Tailwind CSS classes are replaced with Bootstrap classes

Custom animations are implemented with CSS instead of Tailwind directives

State Management:

Authentication state would be handled by PHP sessions instead of React hooks

Dynamic Content:

Data that would come from APIs in React now comes from PHP arrays or database queries

Icons:

Lucide icons are replaced with Bootstrap Icons